      "content": "---\ntitle: 移动互联网创业公司的服务器选择 -- 系统运维 -- IT技术博客大学习 -- 共学习 共进步！\nupdated: 2015-10-07 10:22:59Z\ncreated: 2015-10-07 10:22:59Z\nsource: http://blogread.cn/it/wap/article/6323?f=wb\n---\n\n\n\n<en-note>\n\n&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; background-color: rgb(245, 248, 253); padding: 1px;\">\n\n\n\n&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; clear: both; background-color: rgb(227, 239, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 0px solid rgb(186, 205, 235); padding: 3px; margin: 0px 1px 5px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: bold;\">\n&Tab;<a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/wap/\">IT技术博客大学习 -- 共学习 共进步！</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; padding: 2px 5px; line-height: 30px;\">\n    \n</div>\n\n&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; clear: both; background-color: rgb(227, 239, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 0px solid rgb(186, 205, 235); padding: 3px; margin: 0px 1px 5px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: bold;\">\n&Tab;移动互联网创业公司的服务器选择</div>\n\n\n&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; padding: 2px 5px; line-height: 30px;\">\n\n&Tab;\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\">\n\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;小公司，三五个人，扯开嗓子开干的情况下，不妨参考一下过去我们淌过的坑。<br STYLE=\"\"/></p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong STYLE=\"\">1.网络</strong></p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;在中国，网络成本是比较贵的(包括托管费用)。分析你的目标用户，如果用户是特别集中在南方或者是北方，这能省些钱，多线机房还是很贵的。同时，移动互联网，特别是中国特色的情况下，各种运营商挂js，各种基站网络不通，如果所在的机房在搜索引擎上一条记录都没有的话，那会很惨，基本上你的用户在手机上是很难过去的。\n\n\n<ins STYLE=\"display: inline-block; width: 320px; height: 100px;\"><ins STYLE=\"display: inline-table; border: none; height: 100px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 320px; background-color: transparent;\"><ins STYLE=\"display: block; border: none; height: 100px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 320px; background-color: transparent;\"></ins></ins></ins>\n</p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;如果是百分之百的手机上的应用后端，前期数据量不大的情况下，可以考虑租用一些双线机房的机器。搞大了再自己买机器吧，能省则省。</p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong STYLE=\"\">2.硬件</strong></p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;如果要考虑硬件了，说明你的业务量已经到一个阶段了，当然也不排除高富帅创业过程，上来先来一堆高端服务器的。</p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;内存条：注意你买的机器的主板，主板与内存的配合至关重要。常见的三通道主板，尽可能使用三条相同的内存条，高端四通道主板，使用四条相同内存条。只求大内存，随便加大是没有意义的。</p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;raid卡电池：注意你的raid卡的电池是否加电，是否开启raid cache，这一条在mysql db机器上效果相当明显。</p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;ssd：可以考虑在db机器上使用一部分，app机器上完全不需要。</p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong STYLE=\"\">3.软件</strong>\n\n\n<ins STYLE=\"display: block; height: 280px;\"><ins STYLE=\"display: inline-table; border: none; height: 280px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 361px; background-color: transparent;\"><ins STYLE=\"display: block; border: none; height: 280px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 361px; background-color: transparent;\"></ins></ins></ins>\n                </p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;操作系统：一次开放调查结果显示centos5和centos6是你不二的选择，投票地址在<a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://vote.weibo.com/vid=2087907\">http://vote.weibo.com/vid=2087907</a>。</p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;常规开发的软件：这里有一系列的介绍 &nbsp; <a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://www.54chen.com/document/startup-tech.html\">《谈谈创业公司的技术选型－－朴素的技术观》</a></p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;协议选择：移动互联网特点，手机或者其他手持设备会需要来服务器拿数据，所以这个桥梁的选择也是一个关键的步骤。一般http的穿透率是比较高的，但是要防各种地方运营商的野广告，至于怎么防，一般header头声明为json之类的他们还是不敢夹广告的。</p>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<p STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;综合以上，移动互联才刚刚开始，坑还很深，欢迎互相交流各种坑。<br STYLE=\"\"/></p>&Tab;\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;</div>\n&Tab;\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\">\n&Tab;&Tab;<strong STYLE=\"\">前一篇：</strong><a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/article/6285\">Linux常用性能调优工具索引</a>\n&Tab;</div>\n&Tab;\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important;\">\n&Tab;&Tab;<strong STYLE=\"\">后一篇：</strong><a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/article/6327\">使用tcpdump搞定一个替换问题</a>\n&Tab;</div>&Tab;\n\n&Tab;&Tab;</div> \n\n\n&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; clear: both; background-color: rgb(227, 239, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 0px solid rgb(186, 205, 235); padding: 3px; margin: 0px 1px 5px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: bold;\">\n&Tab;我们猜你喜欢：\n</div>\n\n&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; padding: 2px 5px; line-height: 30px;\">\n&Tab;\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<ol STYLE=\"\">\n\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<li STYLE=\"\"><a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/article/291?f=sa\">通过HttpListener实现轻量级Web服务器[原创] [阅读：2904]</a></li>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<li STYLE=\"\"><a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/article/3106?f=sa\">查看你服务器的安全性 [阅读：2585]</a></li>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<li STYLE=\"\"><a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/article/646?f=sa\">Ruby作为服务器端应用已经成熟了 [阅读：2199]</a></li>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<li STYLE=\"\"><a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/article/3836?f=sa\">图片服务器博客 [阅读：2091]</a></li>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<li STYLE=\"\"><a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/article/745?f=sa\">Linux服务器基本安装 [阅读：2005]</a></li>\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<li STYLE=\"\"><a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/article/621?f=sa\">一个使用PC服务器的高可用性方案介绍 [阅读：1588]</a></li>&Tab;\n&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;</ol>\n\n&Tab;&Tab;</div>\n\n\n&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; clear: both; background-color: rgb(227, 239, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 0px solid rgb(186, 205, 235); padding: 3px; margin: 0px 1px 5px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: bold;\">\n&Tab;文章信息\n</div>\n\n&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; padding: 2px 5px; line-height: 30px;\">\n作者：54chen<br STYLE=\"\"/>来源：<a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" TARGET=\"_blank\" HREF=\"http://www.54chen.com/_linux_/mi-startup-server.html\">五四陈科学院-坚信科学，分享技术</a><br STYLE=\"\"/>时间：2013-04-06 23:17:19<br STYLE=\"\"/>人气：3707<br STYLE=\"\"/></div>\n\n \n\n&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; clear: both; background-color: rgb(227, 239, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 0px solid rgb(186, 205, 235); padding: 3px; margin: 0px 1px 5px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: bold;\">\n&Tab;栏目导航\n</div>\n\n\n&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE=\"font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Luxi Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti !important; padding: 2px 5px; line-height: 30px;\">\n&Tab;<a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/wap/category/2\">PHP</a> | <a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/wap/category/3\">MySQL</a> | <a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/wap/category/4\">Oracle</a> | <a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/wap/category/5\">Linux</a> | <a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/wap/category/6\">Apache</a> | <a STYLE=\"color: rgb(2, 50, 152); text-decoration: none;\" HREF=\"http://blogread.cn/it/wap/categor